snippet: More than a ton of illegal shark fins were seized from a vendor in San Francisco.
abstract: More than a ton of illegal shark fins are seized from Michael Kwong of Kwong Yip Inc, vendor in San Francisco; Kwong is cited for having 2,138 pounds of the fins; possessing shark fins, or selling or trading them, is a misdemeanor in California.
lead_paragraph: More than a ton of illegal shark fins were seized from a vendor in San Francisco.
